OL,3,CPolice urge government to update road
OL,4,Claw after e-scooter collisions
OL,6,FOne of the heads of Jersey's Honorary
OL,7,FPolice is calling on the Government to
OL,8,Fimprove its outdated road traffic
OL,9,Flegislation following two serious
OL,10,Fcollisions between cars and e-scooters.
OL,12,FJoao Camara, St Peter Chef De Police,
OL,13,Fsays the law should be updated to
OL,14,Freflect the changing transport
OL,15,Foptions, giving officers more powers
OL,16,Fto act.
