OL,3,CPolice urge government to update road
OL,4,Claw after e-scooter collisions
OL,6,FHe explains: "There's no doubt it is
OL,7,Ffrustrating, we do need to legislate.
OL,8,FThere are a lot of vehicles on the
OL,9,Froad at the moment which were not
OL,10,Fthought of in 1948 when the Road
OL,11,FTraffic Law was enacted so we need to
OL,12,Fmake sure it keeps pace with these new
OL,13,Fvehicles.
OL,15,FThere is currently no specific law
OL,16,Fpreventing people from using e-
OL,17,Fscooters on roads or public land in
OL,18,FJersey.
