OL,6,FIt is only illegal because they are
OL,7,Fclassed as motorised vehicles so
OL,8,Friders need a licence and insurance
OL,9,Fwhich they cannot get, meaning they
OL,10,Fcan be prosecuted and fined.
OL,12,FE-scooters can be ridden on private
OL,13,Fland with permission but they should
OL,14,Fnot be able to go faster than 15mph.
OL,16,FE-scooters have become more popular in
OL,17,Frecent years with the UK Government
OL,18,Fapproving 30 public hire trials over
OL,19,Fthere - although riding privately
OL,20,Fowned e-scooters on roads is still
OL,21,Fillegal.
