OL,6,FIn Jersey, the island's Infrastructure
OL,7,FMinister says they will look at the
OL,8,Fcurrent legislation.
OL,10,FDeputy Andy Jehan explains: "We've had
OL,11,Fa number of pieces of correspondence
OL,12,Ffrom States Members and the public.
OL,13,FI've spoken to ministers and we're
OL,14,Fgoing to discuss it."
OL,16,FRiders say e-scooters offer a quick
OL,17,Fand easy way to travel and can be safe
OL,18,Fif used in the right way.
